'''哈米克反应'''（{{lang-en|Hammick reaction}}），得名於英国化学家[[达尔齐尔·哈米克|达尔齐尔·哈米克]]，指在[[羰基化合物|羰基化合物]]存在下，α-[[吡啶甲酸|吡啶甲酸]]及其类似物受热转变为2-[[吡啶|吡啶]]基[[原醇|原醇]]。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Dyson, P.; Hammick, D. L. | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.|J. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1937 | pages = 1724 | doi = 10.1039/jr9370001724 | title = 362. Experiments on the mechanism of decarboxylation. Part I. Decomposition of quinaldinic and isoquinaldinic acids in the presence of compounds containing carbonyl groups}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = Hammick, D. L.; Dyson, P. | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.|J. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1939 | pages = 809 | doi = 10.1039/jr9390000809 | title = 172. The mechanism of decarboxylation. Part II. The production of cyanide-like ions from α-picolinic, quinaldinic, and isoquinaldinic acids}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = Brown, E. V.; Shambhu, M. B. | title = Hammick reaction of methoxypyridine-2-carboxylic acids with benzaldehyde. Preparation of methoxy-2-pyridyl phenyl ketones | journal = [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]] | year = 1971 | volume = 36 | pages = 2002 | doi = 10.1021/jo00813a034 }}</ref>

[[Image:Hammick_Reaction_Scheme.png|center]]

用[[对异丙基甲苯|对异丙基甲苯]]作溶剂可提高反应产率。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Sperber, N.; Papa, D.; Schwenk, E.; Sherlock, M. | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1949 | volume = 71 | pages = 887 | doi = 10.1021/ja01171a034 | title = Pyridyl-Substituted Alkamine Ethers as Antihistaminic Agents}}</ref>

==反应机理==
加热时，α-吡啶甲酸发生[[脱羧|脱羧]]，生成[[两性离子|两性离子]](2)。该离子与强[[亲电试剂|亲电试剂]]（如[[醛|醛]]）作用，发生对羰基的[[亲核加成|亲核加成]]。加成产物发生质子转移，便得到原醇(4)。

